    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\n`ex_detach()` has a stub for `:detach!` that errors with `\"bang (!) not supported yet\"`. There is no way for one UI to kick the others off a shared Nvim server.\n\n### Solution\n\n`:detach!` disconnects every UI except the caller's, keeping the server running and the caller attached. No-op with one UI. Errors with `E5768: No UI attached` when no UI is attached.",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
